es.org/epig10002201\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl>\n                        \u003Cauthor>Alessio\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>1970\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange>61\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"http://zotero.org/groups/382445/items/5X3JK8SE\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002566\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002566\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl>\n                        \u003Cauthor>Lejeune\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>1970\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange>147, 156, 160\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"http://zotero.org/groups/382445/items/2H7NP37F\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001880\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001880\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl>\n                        \u003Cauthor>Schmoll\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>1961\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange>68\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"http://zotero.org/groups/382445/items/EBTAVEAP\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001602\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001602\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl>\n                        \u003Cauthor>Tusa\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>1960\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange>no.11\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"http://zotero.org/groups/382445/items/W57IFXNR\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001542\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001542\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                \u003C/listBibl>\n                \u003ClistBibl type=\"discussion\">\n              